Description:
While Electrosurge is active, randomly uses one of the following attacks at intervals of <color=#f39001>2</color>s:
1. <color=#b863ee>Thundercloud Strike</color>: Deals <color=#b863ee>Electro DMG</color> to opponents within the AoE, and the active character gains <color=#f39001>2</color> Elemental Energy;
2. <color=#0075de>Thundercloud Rainstorm</color>: Deals <color=#0075de>Hydro DMG</color> to opponents within the AoE, and the active character is healed for <color=#f39001>5%</color> HP
